OL,3,CDangerous driver caused head on crash
OL,4,Cwhich led to woman losing a leg
OL,6,FA dangerous driver has been jailed for
OL,7,Fa head-on collision in North Yorkshire
OL,8,Fwhich left a woman in a coma and
OL,9,Fneeding to have her leg amputated.
OL,11,FSharon Odell, 55, from Pickering, says
OL,12,Fthe accident means she can no longer
OL,13,Fdo the things she enjoys most, such as
OL,14,Fcountry walks with her family and dog.
