OL,6,FShe was airlifted to hospital in a
OL,7,Fcritical condition where she remained
OL,8,Fin a coma for two and a half weeks
OL,9,Fafter the accident in April last year.
OL,10,FHer injuries were so severe that she
OL,11,Funderwent multiple operations,
OL,12,Fincluding having a leg amputated.
OL,14,FIn her Victim Personal Statement read
OL,15,Fout at the sentencing of Milosz Danisz
OL,16,FMalkowski at York Crown Court, Mrs
OL,17,FOdell said:
OL,19,F"I can't begin to comprehend how
OL,20,Feveryone who is close to me felt
OL,21,Fwhilst I was in a coma."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
