OL,3,CDangerous driver caused head on crash
OL,4,Cwhich led to woman losing a leg
OL,6,F"All of this has not only affected me
OL,7,Fbut it has also had a big impact on
OL,8,Feveryone around me, my immediate
OL,9,Ffamily, work colleagues and the
OL,10,Fchildren I work with at school.
OL,12,F"I am not able to do the things I
OL,13,Fenjoy most, like country walks with my
OL,14,Ffamily and walk my dog. I also feel
OL,15,Fthat I can't do my job to my full
OL,16,Fability, like playing games like
OL,17,Ffootball and dodgeball with the
OL,18,Fchildren I work with."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
