OL,3,CDangerous driver caused head on crash
OL,4,Cwhich led to woman losing a leg
OL,6,FMrs Odell was driving her blue VW on
OL,7,Fthe A170 near Thornton le Dale on 17
OL,8,FApril last year when 34-year-old
OL,9,FMalkowski , from Scarborough, ploughed
OL,10,Finto her in his silver VW Passat car.
OL,12,FHe was travelling in the opposite
OL,13,Fdirection when he performed an
OL,14,Fovertake of a car and a coach.
OL,16,FDespite Mrs Odell's vehicle being
OL,17,Fvisible, he failed to return to his
OL,18,Flane in time and caused a head-on
OL,19,Fcrash with extensive damage to both
OL,20,Fvehicles.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
