OL,3,CDangerous driver caused head on crash
OL,4,Cwhich led to woman losing a leg
OL,6,FA detailed investigation was conducted
OL,7,Fby Roads Policing Officers who
OL,8,Festablished that the lead up to the
OL,9,Fcollision was captured on the dashcam
OL,10,Fwithin Malkowski's vehicle.
OL,12,FForensic Collision work was also used
OL,13,Fto reconstruct the collision, and
OL,14,Fofficers were able to evidence the
OL,15,Fpositions of the vehicles when it
OL,16,Foccurred.
OL,18,FThis showed that Mrs Odell had done
OL,19,Fher best to avoid the collision but
OL,20,Fwas unable to do so.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
