OL,4,Cwhich led to woman losing a leg
OL,6,FFaced with the overwhelming evidence
OL,7,Fagainst him, Malkowski, who also
OL,8,Fsuffered serious injuries in the
OL,9,Fcollision, pleaded guilty at the
OL,10,Fearliest opportunity.
OL,12,FAt York Crown Court he was sentenced
OL,13,Fto 18 months' imprisonment and handed
OL,14,Fa two-year, nine month driving ban.
OL,16,FHe will be required to pass an
OL,17,Fextended test to regain his driving
OL,18,Flicence.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
