OL,6,F"Traffic Constable Isaac Carter, of
OL,7,FNorth Yorkshire Police's Roads
OL,8,FPolicing Group, who led the
OL,9,Finvestigation, said: "Nothing will
OL,10,Fever make up for the dreadful, life-
OL,11,Fchanging injuries Mrs Odell suffered
OL,12,Fthat day and the difficulties it
OL,13,Fcontinues to have on her day-to-day
OL,14,Flife.
OL,16,F"I just hope the outcome at court
OL,17,Fprovides some measure of comfort to
OL,18,Fher and her family, knowing that the
OL,19,Fperson responsible for the trauma has
OL,20,Fadmitted his guilt and been sent to
OL,21,Fprison.
