OL,6,F"As for Malkowski and other dangerous
OL,7,Fdrivers on our roads, this case
OL,8,Fhighlights the unnecessary nature of
OL,9,Fthe overtake and how decision making
OL,10,Fin those few seconds can have a life-
OL,11,Flong impact on the victim and their
OL,12,Floved-ones."
